accg 1
aero 1
fric 70
elas 20
mvto game "CreatorX" game "CreatorY"


**
** VENDOR PUSH SCRIPT
**

scrp 2 23 21824 1
	lock
	doif from ne pntr
		stim writ from 90 1
	endi

	setv va00 rand 0 8
	setv va01 va00
	addv va01 1
	mulv va00 4
	addv va00 5
	setv va01 posx
	setv va02 post
	addv va02 115
	anim [ 0 1 2 3 4 ]
	over
	inst
	new: simp 2 va01 21824 "elevator_vendor_UZAG" 4 va00 rand 1500 2500
** attr: mouseable 2 + collide 64 + physics 128 = 194
** bhvr: pickup 16 + eat 32 = 48
	attr 194
	bhvr 48
** Set category as elevator (26)
	cato 26
** Will go through some walls
	perm 60
** Physics
	accg 1
	aero 1
	fric 70
	elas 20
	tick 1000
	slow
	mvsf va01 va02
	targ ownr
	anim [ 4 3 2 1 0 ]
	over
	unlk
endm



